text: Love the tenderness of the beef I ordered drizzle with the creamy cheese. Ate twice and can't get enough it! Going back for more.. a bit pricey but worth the value so jus take my money~~~ ðŸ˜œ
Waited one hour for food everybody that ordered after got their food first, went to check food was not even made only after checking did they start preparing my food
Chicken kebab burger is delicious. Meat is tender, generous sauce makes the burger so juicy. $6nett. Limited parking.

This is one of the best place I've eaten at.  The only reason I have given this place 3 stars is because of its pricing in relation to it's food. To me I see the the quantity of the food to it's pricing to be not so worth it as the price does not correlate to the food quality.  A reduction of the food prices by $2 could bring in the crowd.  Yeah I know people still buy from your shop however bringing down the prices of the food will really help out in terms of food sales in quantity as this isn't a high class restaurant.
Ordered cheesy chicken & nasi goreng kampung. Nasi goreng taste not bad. Cheesy chicken can have a stronger cheese taste. Price for western food towards the higher side given the environment
